se%20writers%20are%20commonly%20employed%20in%20the%20computer%2C%20science%2C%20and%20tech%20sectors%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Foes%2Fcurrent%2Foes273042.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eearn%20a%20mean%20annual%20salary%20of%20%2486%2C760%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20an%20average%20of%20%2441.71%20an%20hour%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20not%20always%20required%2C%20candidates%20typically%20need%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20to%20enter%20the%20field%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20to%20have%20a%20technical%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Bingo%20manager%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResponsible%20for%20overseeing%20and%20managing%20bingo%20games%20at%20a%20casino%2C%20game%20hall%2C%20or%20parlor%2C%20this%20individual%20approves%20jackpots%20and%20payouts%20in%20accordance%20with%20all%20local%2C%20state%2C%20and%20federal%20regulations%20to%20ensure%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20recent%20information%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FSalary.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESalary.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bingo%20managers%20can%20earn%20between%20%2451%2C965%20and%20%24112%2C599%20a%20year%2C%20with%20a%20mean%20salary%20of%20%2470%2C241.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20high-school%20diploma%20or%20its%20equivalent%20may%20be%20required%2C%20along%20with%20three%20to%20five%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Heavy%20and%20tractor-trailer%20truck%20driver%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20long-haul%20drivers%20are%20responsible%20for%20transporting%20goods%2C%20which%20may%20include%20hazardous%20waste%2C%20over%20intercity%20routes%20that%20often%20span%20several%20states%2C%20in%20trucks%20that%20typically%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%