0a%20few%20of%20the%20fun%20features%20in%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20The%20enchanted%20forest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22965%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Enchanted%20forest%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c02354bea34400196175d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20center%20of%20the%20house%20doesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20natural%20light%2C%20so%20I%20used%20that%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20create%20an%20indoor%20enchanted%20forest.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Blumberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20create%20a%20transition%20between%20the%20foyer%2C%20the%20parlor%20and%20the%20staircase.%20To%20create%20this%20space%2C%20I%20felt%20inspired%20by%20the%20one%20scene%20that%20had%20a%20forest%20with%20butterflies%20in%20%26quot%3BA%20Midsummer%20Night's%20Dream.%26quot%3B%20As%20I%20watched%20it%2C%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20happy%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20recreate%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brought%20in%20a%20friend%20to%20do%20the%20mural%20on%20the%20staircase%20walls.%20I%20also%20added%20in%20taxidermy%20owls%20that%20my%20husband%20collected%20growing%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20forest%20is%20made%20from%20real%20trees%20and%20I%20applied%20fake%20leaves%20and%20blossoms.%20Still%2C%20it%20looked%20too%20naked%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20added%20in%202%2C000%20butterflies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20The%20casket%20bar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22754%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22casket%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c023faed4f460019637c35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22566%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20decided%20to%20have%20some%20fun%20with%20the%20history%20of%20the%20house%2C%20and%20turn%20it%20in%20to%20a%20bar%20that%20can%20be%20called%20up%20to%204%20different%20floors%20in%20the%20house.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Blumberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2