ue%20space.%3Cp%3EHeather%20Blumberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20dining%20room%20used%20to%20be%20a%20chapel%2C%20so%20it's%20really%20a%20huge%20space.%20Everything%20is%20black%2C%20and%20when%20people%20walk%20through%20it%20they%20always%20have%20a%20moment%20where%20they%20take%20it%20all%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20probably%20use%20the%20kitchen%20and%20family%20room%20the%20most.%20We're%20a%20disgustingly%20close-knit%20family%2C%20and%20we%20like%20to%20hang%20out%20together%2C%20eat%20together%20and%20do%20game%20nights%20more%20often%20than%20we%20probably%20should.%20We%20all%20love%20cooking%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThis%20house%20also%20has%20supernatural%20activity%20in%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20you%20see%20people%20walking%20around%2C%20and%20you%20hear%20footsteps%20or%20doors%20opening.%20More%20specifically%20we%20have%20a%20woman%20that%20just%20shouts%20%26quot%3BHello!%26quot%3B%20randomly.%20The%20first%20time%20it%20happened%2C%20I%20was%20scared.%20I%20sat%20in%20a%20room%20for%20about%20three%20hours%20afterwards%2C%20not%20daring%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20it's%20normal%20and%20happens%20all%20the%20time.%20There's%20nothing%20scary%20about%20it%3B%20we%20don't%20have%20demons%20trying%20to%20take%20our%20souls%2C%20or%20anything%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20I%20can't%20wait%20to%20work%20on%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20home%20like%20the%20main%20library.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20house%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20B%26amp%3BB.%20I%20also%20want%20to%20go%20off%20and%20work%20on%20an%20asylum%20or%20a%20hospital%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20fun%2C%20unique%20home%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20email%20Alyshia%20Hull%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aahull%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eahull%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%