chive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20nascent%20technology%20could%20also%20cause%20massive%20upheaval%20if%20it%20causes%20huge%20numbers%20of%20job%20losses%2C%20and%20could%20do%20enormous%20damage%20to%20the%20world%20if%20it's%20used%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%2C%20Buffett%20cautioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHere%20are%20Buffett's%207%20best%20quotes%20about%20AI%2C%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E1.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20got%20great%20potential.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20how%20much%20better%20results%20can%20you%20get%20with%20it%20than%20using%20human%20beings%2C%20or%20how%20many%20human%20being%20can%20you%20replace%20in%20getting%20it%3F%20Or%20can%20you%20get%20some%20entirely%20new%20form%20of%20information%20that%20humans%20are%20actually%20incapable%20of%20getting%2C%20because%20they%20can't%20keep%20every%20word%20that's%20been%20written%20about%20prostate%20cancer%20or%20something%20up%20to%20yesterday%20in%20their%20minds%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20look%20at%20X-rays%20much%20better%20and%20faster%20than%20humans%20can%2C%20and%20read%20all%20the%20literature%2C%20zillions%20of%20pages.%20But%20the%20biggest%20value%20will%20be%20when%20it%20actually%20replaces%20human%20labor.%20Machines%20don't%20come%20round%20annually%20and%20ask%20for%20higher%20wages%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20need%20healthcare%20besides%20a%20little%20maintenance.%20If%20they%20replace%20people%20in%20a%20big%20way%2C%20it%20would%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20result%20in%20significantly%20less%20employment%20in%20certain%20areas.%20We'd%20work%20a%20lot%20less%20hours%20a%20week.%20And%20that's%20enormously%20prosocial%2C%20eventually.%20It's%20enormously%20disruptive%20in%20other%20ways.%20And%20it%20can%20have%20huge%20problems%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20democracy%20and%20how%20it%20reacts%20to%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20knowing%20a%20thing%20about%20it%2C%20I%20would%20think%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20would%20have%20that%20hugely%20beneficial%20social%20effect%2C%20but%20a%20very%20unpredictable%20political%20effect%20if%20it%20came%20in%20fast%2C%20which%20I%20think%20it%20could.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BWouldn't%20it%20be%20wonderful%20if%20someday%20we%20got%20to%20the%20point%20where%20there%20are%20robots%20everyplace.%20They%20were%20running%20farms%2C%20they%20were%20running%20Apple%2C%20they%20were%20running%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20%E2%80%94%20and%20all%20you%20had%20to%20do%20was%20one%20person%20could%20punch%20a%20button%20at%20the%20start%20of%20every%20morning%2C%20and%20all%20the%20goods%20and%20services%20that%20we're%20getting%20now%20would%20be%20turned%20out%20by%20robots%2C%20or%20whatever%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20something%20can%20do%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%2C%20I%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20worried%20because%20I%20know%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20un-invent%20it.%20We%20did%20invent%2C%20for%20a%20very%2C%20very%20good%20reason%2C%20the%20atom%20bomb%20in%20World%20War%20II.%20Einstein%20said%2C%20'This%20has%20changed%20everything%20in%20the%20world%20except%20how%20men%20think.'%20With%20AI%2C%20it%20can%20change%20everything%20in%20the%20world%20except%20how%20men%20think%20and%20behave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%26quot%3BI've%20got%20the%20cure%20for%20it%2C%20I'm%2086.%20You%20don't%20worry%20as%20much%20under%20those%20circumstances.%26quot%3B%20(Buffett%20was%20addressing%20concerns%20about%20AI%20rebelling%20against%20its%20creators%20and%20behaving%20maliciously.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonus%20quote%20from%20Buffett's%20business%20partner%2C%20Charlie%20Munger%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20personally%20skeptical%20of%20some%20of%20the%20hype%20that%20has%20gone%20into%20artificial%20intelligence.%20I%20think%20old-fashioned%20intelligence%20works%20pretty%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%