20have%20been%20upbeat%20so%20far%20%E2%80%93%20with%20almost%204%20in%205%20companies%20exceeding%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarnings%20may%20continue%20to%20surpass%20Wall%20Street%20expectations%2C%20fueling%20the%20stock-market%20rally%2C%20according%20to%20State%20Street.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChief%20investment%20strategist%20Michael%20W.%20Arone%20lists%20five%20reasons%20why%20earnings%20may%20continue%20to%20top%20estimates.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20second-quarter%20earnings%20reports%20have%20shown%20an%20upbeat%20trend%20so%20far%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnearly-4-in-5-companies-have-posted-q2-earnings-that-beat-estimates-2023-7%5C%22%3Ealmost%204%20in%205%20companies%20exceeding%20Wall%20Street%20expectations%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20of%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20continue%2C%20supporting%20the%20buoyancy%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20according%20to%20State%20Street%2C%20the%20the%20world's%20fourth%20largest%20asset%20manager.%20The%20benchmark%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20of%20US%20shares%20has%20advanced%20almost%203%25%20in%20July%2C%20taking%20its%20year-to-date%20gains%20to%2019%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20W.%20Arone%2C%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20State%20Street%2C%20lists%20five%20reasons%20why%20US%20corporate%20earnings%20may%20continue%20to%20beat%20estimates%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20earnings%20to%20grow%2C%20excluding%20energy%20and%20materials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarnings%20for%20energy%20and%20materials%20are%20forecasted%20to%20contract%20YoY%20by%2045%25%20and%2028%25.%20If%20you%20exclude%20these%20two%20sectors%20that%20make%20up%20just%206.5%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20the%20index%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20grow%20earnings%20by%20about%201.5%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Arone%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20research%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Any%20weakness%20is%20concentrated%20in%20'largest%20cap%20names'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20median%20calculations%2C%20and%20not%20the%20mean%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20earnings%20per%20share%20would%20grow%20by%20just%20over%201%25.%20The%20index%20is%20overweighted%20on%20mega-cap%20tech%20stocks%2C%20which%20have%20disproportionately%20driven%20growth.%20But%20analysts%20may%20demand%20too%20much%20of%20these%20giants%2C%20while%20overlooking%20the%20index's%20wider%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Revenues%20may%20be%20lower%2C%20but%20so%20are%20expectations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EArone%20believes%20that%20the%20market%20consensus%20for%20revenue%20declines%20across%20the%20board%20has%20set%20earnings%20expectations%20low%20%E2%80%93%20allowing%20companies%20to%20continue%20beating%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20beating%2C%20and%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20beat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20based%20on%20history%2C%20they're%20likely%20to%20beat%20in%20the%204%20to%205%25%20range%20in%20aggregate%20on%20average%2C%20possibly%20more.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Tech%20stocks%20are%20expected%20to%20outpace%20the%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETechnology%20names%20are%20expected%20to%20outdo%20the%20market%20after%20%26quot%3Bfive%20quarters%20of%20weak%20EPS%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20ac%20ccording%20to%20the%20strategist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20sheer%20size%20of%20this%20sector%20in%20market-cap%20terms%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20mega-cap%20stocks%20currently%20driving%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20returns%20%E2%80%93%20such%20outperformance%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20a%20major%20tailwind%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20market%2C%20Arone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Earnings%20growth%20to%20continue%20in%20Q3%20and%20Q4%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BEarnings%20growth%20is%20expected%20in%20the%20third%20and%20