0Mosque%20today%20told%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20fears%20that%20the%20historic%20structure%20might%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20court%2C%20which%20asked%20the%20petitioners%20how%20they%20will%20trust%20the%20court's%20ruling%20that%20if%20they%20cannot%20trust%20the%20ASI's%20assurances%20that%20there%20will%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20court%2C%20the%20mosque%20committee%20said%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20has%20stood%20at%20the%20place%2C%20next%20to%20the%20iconic%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20for%201%2C000%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20submissions%20that%20it%20trusts%20a%20survey%20similar%20to%20one%20that%20happened%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20case%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20mosque%20committee%C2%A0said%20the%20circumstances%20in%20the%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20dispute%20case%20were%20different%20and%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20comparison%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20talk%20of%20a%20temple%20under%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20is%20fictional%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioners'%20counsel%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20imagination%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20allowing%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20ASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20has%20claimed%20that%20a%20temple%20constructed%20at%20the%20site%20in%201585%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20Raja%20Todarmal%20was%20demolished%20in%201669.%20A%20group%20of%20Hindu%20women%20have%20now%20sought%20permission%20to%20worship%20the%20deities%20there%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20said%20that%20the%20women%20petitioners%20had%20told%20a%20lower%20court%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20proof%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20inside%20the%20mosque%20complex%20and%20that%20the%20ASI%20must%20gather%20them.%20%26quot%3BThis%20cannot%20be%20allowed.%20You%20cannot%20ask%20someone%20else%20to%20gather%20proof.%20This%20is%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20challenging%20the%20lower%20court's%20direction%20for%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20stressed%20that%20they%20have%20proof%20and%20added%20that%20an%20ASI%20survey%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20expert%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asked%20the%20Hindu%20side%20if%20excavation%20was%20necessary%2C%20tits%20counsel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20but%20this%20won't%20be%20inside%20the%20mosque.%20ASI%20will%20do%20radar%20mapping.%20Excavation%20will%20also%20be%20conducted%20if%20circumstances%20demand%2C%20that%20too%20in%20the%20last%20stage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20submissions%20on%20how%20this%20excavation%20will%20be%20conducted%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEither%20you%20videograph%20the%20survey%20or%20submit%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20mosque.%26quot%3B%20The%20Hindu%20side's%20counsel%20agreed%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20mosque%20committee%20said%20it%20does%20not%20trust%20the%20assurances%2C%20the%20court%20retorted%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20don't%20trust%20anyone%2C%20how%20will%20you%20trust%20our%20ruling%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20responded%20sharply%20to%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20submission%20that%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20lawyer%20would%20be%20responsible%20if%20the%20structure%20falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20asks%20if%20the%20mosque%20committee%20fears%20that%20the%20structure%20may%20fall%2C%20the%20committee%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20might%2C%20it%20is%201%2C000%20years%20old.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20assurances%20that%20no%20survey%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20area%20sealed%20under%20orders%20from%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20mosque%20committee%20said%20that%20area%20will%20also%20suffer%20damage%20if%20the%20survey%20is%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Hindu%20side's%20submission%20that%20the%20ASI%20team%20is%20waiting%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Pritinker%20Diwaker%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20satisfied%20with%20what%20you%20are%20going%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20submission%20that%20the%20structure%20won't%20be%20damaged%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20going%20to%20drill%20or%20is%20it%20like%20a%20vacuum%20cleaner%3F%20Have%20you%20ever%20done%20this%20work%20earlier%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ASI%20said%20they%20have%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%20if%20there%20are%20photos%20of%20those%20projects.%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20is%20putting%20strong%20doubts%20to%20the%20work%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20side%20said%20the%20machine%20used%20%26quot%3Bwill%20move%20like%20a%20lawn%20mower%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20machines%20are%20accepted%20all%20over%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20resume%20the%20hearing%20at%204.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20hit%20headlines%20in%202021%20after%20a%20group%20of%20Hindu%20women%20approached%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20court%20for%20permission%20to%20worship%20deities%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lower%20court%20then%20ordered%20a%20video%20survey%20of%20the%20complex%20during%20which%20an%20object%20was%20discovered%20that%20a%20section%20of%20people%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20shivling.%20The%20mosque%20management%20committee%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20fountain%20in%20the%20wazookhana%20(pool)%20to%20wash%20hands%20and%20feet%20before%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20issue%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20sealed%20off%20the%20pool%20(wazookhana).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20mosque%20committee's%20petition%20that%20challenge%20the%20maintainability%20of%20the%20request%20to%20worship%20Hindu%20deities%20found%20inside%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20a%20Varanasi%20court's%20ruling%2C%20allowing%20a%20survey%20by%20the%20ASI%20inside%20the%20mosque%20complex%20except%20the%20pool%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20expressing%20concerns%20regarding%20excavation%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20now%20allowed%20the%20petitioners%20to%20approach%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20to%20challenge%20the%20order%20for%20the%20ASI%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690358280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F6tbusq7o_gyanvapi-mosque-650_625x300_13_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20survey%20by%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%2C%20the%20management%20committee%20of%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20today%20told%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20that%20it%20fears%20that%20the%20historic%20structure%20might%20fall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-fears-4240992%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-allahabad-high-court-mosque-might-fall-in-gyanvapi-court-hearing-muslim-side-flags-