20vegetarian%20and%20non-veg%20food%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty%20mentioned%20that%20while%20she%20is%20adventurous%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20her%20work%2C%20she%20is%20not%20the%20same%20regarding%20her%20food%20choices.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20pure%20vegetarian%2C%20I%20don't%20even%20eat%20eggs%2C%20or%20garlic.%20What%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20is%2C%20that%20the%20same%20spoon%20will%20be%20used%20for%20both%2C%20vegetarian%20and%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20It%20weighs%20on%20my%20mind%20a%20lot!%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murty%20admitted.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20when%20she%20travels%20abroad%2C%20she%20seeks%20out%20vegetarian%20restaurants%20or%20prepares%20her%20own%20meals.%20She%20carries%20her%20own%20bag%20of%20food%20and%20cooking%20items%20that%20can%20be%20easily%20heated%20in%20water%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2p9z6pXhQOU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murty's%20comments%20have%20trigged%20various%20reactions%20online.%20While%20some%20internet%20users%20agreed%20that%20carrying%20food%20from%20home%20indeed%20is%20a%20good%20practice%2C%20others%20begged%20to%20differ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20Indians%20pack%20food%20while%20travelling%20abroad.%20Food%20is%20a%20choice.%20%23sudhamurthy%20is%20any%20elderly%20woman%20in%20our%20household%20who%20likes%20to%20chat%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20judge%20people%20based%20on%20their%20food%20preferences%20or%20other%20personal%20habits.%20Instead%2C%20we%20should%20focus%20on%20treating%20everyone%20with%20respect%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20caste%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20%2C%20Aunt%20and%20even%20my%20wife%20takes%20food%20while%20travelling%20international%20as%20they%20are