rcement%20Directorate%20in%20November%202018.%20He%20was%20to%20retire%20two%20years%20later%2C%20after%20turning%2060%2C%20but%20the%20government%20gave%20him%20an%20extension%20in%20November%202020.%20%C2%A0His%20term%20was%20extended%20twice%20after%20that%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20extension%20was%20till%20November%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2011%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20termed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chiefs-extension-illegal-can-stay-till-july-31-court-4196638%5C%22%3Ethird%20extension%3C%2Fa%3E%20given%20to%20Mr%20Mishra%20illegal%20and%20said%20that%20it%20violated%20a%202021%20judgment%20of%20the%20court.%20However%2C%20it%20let%20him%20continue%20till%20July%2031%20after%20the%20centre%20expressed%20concern%20about%20continuity%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20peer%20review%20by%20the%20global%20terror%20financing%20watchdog%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force.%20The%20government%20was%20asked%20to%20appoint%20a%20new%20director%20of%20the%20probe%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20judgment%2C%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Randeep%20Surjewala%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20one%20of%20the%20petitions%20in%20the%20case%2C%20claimed%20it%20had%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bmisusing%26quot%3B%20agencies%20to%20destabilise%20elected%20governments%20in%20non-BJP-ruled%20states%20and%20target%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20victory%20of%20justice%20and%20vindication%20of%20our%20stand%20on%20brazen%20misuse%20and%20compromise%20of%20ED%20for%20political%20vendetta%20as%20also%20the%20blatant%20pursuit%20of%20Modi%20government's%20desperate%20and%20obvious%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Surjewala%20had%20said%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20serious%20and%20historic%20indictment%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20was%20so%20desperate%20to%20have%20its%20ch