20at%2011%20am%20on%20the%20fifth%20day%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%2C%20the%20agenda%20included%20statements%20from%20Union%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20Standing%20Committee%20Recommendations%2C%20a%20proposed%20amendment%20to%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Act%2C%201969%2C%20and%20a%20motion%20for%20election%20to%20the%20council%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20has%20stated%20its%20readiness%20for%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20Manipur%20situation%2C%20although%20opposition%20parties%20are%20pressing%20for%20a%20debate%20under%20a%20rule%20that%20would%20require%20a%20vote.%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20opposition%20leaders%20in%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%2C%20asserting%20the%20government's%20willingness%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20and%20urging%20bipartisan%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690355400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvolacgo8_mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-after-rajya-sabha-mic-turned-off-my-self-respect-challenged-4240845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20MPs%20introduced%20notices%20in%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seeking%20discussion%20on%20the%20ongoing%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-after-rajya-sabha-mic-turned-off-my-self-respect-challenged-4240845%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-after-rajya-sabha-mic-turned-off-my-self-respect-challenged-4240845%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-after-rajya-sabha-mic-turned-off-my-self-respect-challenged-4240845%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Challenges%20For%20'Friends-With-Benefits'%20BJP%20And%20JD(S)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20election%20results%20have%20brought%20together%20strange%20bedfellows%20trying%20to%20forge%20a%20united%20opposition%20in%20the%20state.%20Despite%20ideological%20differences%2C%20the%20proximity%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20is%20growing.%20Top%20leaders%20from%20both%20the%20parties%20have%20backed%20each%20other%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20and%20on%20public%20platforms.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20questions%20on%20when%20the%20two%20parties%20will%20formally%20announce%20their%20strategy%20for%20next%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20There%20have%20always%20been%20broad%20hints%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20could%20join%20the%20NDA%20camp%20any%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20JD(S)%20from%20the%20NDA%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20last%20week%20raised%20many%20eyebrows.%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20who%20had%20clearly%20shown%20his%20preference%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20the%20meet%2C%20apparently%20due%20to%20strong%20opposition%20from%20a%20section%20of%20Karnataka%20BJP%20leaders.%20The%20BJP's%20national%20leadership%20wants%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20to%20boost%20its%20prospects%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20drubbing%20in%20the%20state%20election%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20former%20chief%20minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20of%20the%20BJP%20who%20first%20indicated%20that%20both%20the%20parties%20were%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20forming%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20is%20repeatedly%20saying%20the%20JD(S)%20and%20the%20BJP%20will%20work%20together%20in%20Karnataka.%20At%20a%20recent%20legislature%20party%20meeting%2C%20JD(S)%20supremo%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda%20allowed%20his%20son%20Kumaraswamy%20to%20decide%20on%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20patriarch%20urged%20his%20party%20members%20to%20work%20with%20his%20son%2C%20who%20will%20ultimately%20decide%20on%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20right%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%2025%20of%20Karnataka's%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20A%20repeat%20performance%20seems%20elusive%20for%20the%20party%20at%20a%20time%20the%20state%20Congress%20government%20is%20doing%20everything%20possible%20to%20implement%20its%20manifesto%20promises%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3BFive%20Guarantees%26quot%3B%20programme.%20BJP%20leaders%20-%20both%20at%20the%20national%20and%20state%20level%20-%20feel%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20will%20brighten%20their%20electoral%20chances%20in%20the%20Vokkaligga%20belt%20of%20South%20Karnataka%2C%20besides%20spoiling%20the%20Congress's%20prospects%20in%20the%20region.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20formation%20of%20'INDIA'%2C%20the%20coalition%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20has%20rejuvenated%20Karnataka%20Congress%20leaders%20who%20are%20working%20with%20a%20vengeance%20for%20a%20repeat%20performance%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20there%20are%20challenges%20to%20the%20alliance%20from%20both%20sides.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20going%20through%20a%20leadership%20crisis.%20In%20the%20days%20of%20BS%20Yeddyurappa%2C%20the%20party's%20face%20was%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20The%20BJP%20lacks%20a%20strong%2C%20charismatic%20local%20party%20leader%20acceptable%20to%20all%20sects%20and%20cadre%20alike%2C%20who%20can%20make%20the%20national%20leadership%20understand%20the%20region's%20political%20and%20social%20nuances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20is%20averse%20to%20an%20alliance%20or%20a%20merger%20of%20the%20parties%20as%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20crisis%20in%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20common%20legislature%20party%20and%20electing%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20as%20the%20opposition%20leader%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20These%20leaders%20feel%20it%20will%20demoralise%20the%20party%20cadre%20further%20after%20the%20recent%20defeat%20in%20state%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20a%20strong%20cadre%20across%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20ceding%20its%20advantages%20or%20sharing%20it%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20will%20confuse%20the%20workers%20as%20well%20as%20BJP%20constituents.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20the%20JD(S)%20and%20Congress%20came%20together%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20could%20win%20just%20one%20seat%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20fine%20with%20the%20alliance%20but%20its%20leaders%20feel%20the%20JD(S)%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20two.%20As%20of%20today%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20has%20just%20one%20seat%20-%20Hassan%2C%20from%20where%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20Deve%20Gowda's%20grandson%2C%20won%20in%202019.%20But%20within%20an%20alliance%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20can%20demand%20at%20least%20five%20seats%20-%20Mandya%2C%20Hassan%2C%20Kolar%2C%20Tumakuru%2C%20Bangalore%20Rural%20or%20Mysuru%20-%20and%20can%20win%20three%20to%20four%20seats.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20it%20is%20an%20existential%20crisis%20from%20which%20it%20is%20making%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20to%20emerge.%20The%20grapevine%20has%20it%20that%20there%20was%20a%20discussion%20within%20the%20JD(S)%20for%20a%20merger%20with%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20wants%20to%20keep%20his%20options%20open%2C%20and%20is%20unlikely%20to%20hesitate%20in%20jumping%20ship%20when%20the%20time%20is%20right.%20For%20now%2C%20his%20reason%20for%20not%20merging%20is%20that%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20upset%20his%20father%20and%20JD(S)%20founder%2C%20Deve%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20to%20the%20coalition%20will%20be%20that%20the%20JD(S)%20has%20traditionally%20reached%20out%20to%20Muslim%20voters%2C%20which%2C%20in%20case%20of%20a%20shift%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20will%20be%20a%20lost%20constituency%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20tandem%2C%20both%20Bommai%20and%20Kumaraswamy%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20Bangalore%20Mysore%20Infrastructure%20Corridor%20(BMIC)%20from%20NICE%20(Nandi%20Infrastructure%20Corridor%20Enterprises)%2C%20and%20alleged%20that%20it%20had%20collected%20Rs%201%2C325%20crore%20illegally%20from%20motorists%20in%20form%20of%20road%20tolls.%20Both%20the%20parties%20came%20together%20to%20denounce%20the%20Congress%20government's%20act%20of%20deploying%20IAS%20officers%20to%20receive%20and%20host%20leaders%20of%20opposition%20parties%20for%20their%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%20earlier.%20They%20collectively%20stopped%20the%20government%20from%20passing%20the%20APMC%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20in%20the%20legislative%20council%2C%20where%20no%20party%20has%20a%20majority.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20that%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20boycotted%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20reply%20to%20the%20Budget%20debate%20during%20assembly%20proceedings.%20Kumaraswamy%20also%20listed%20out%20the%20inadequacies%20in%20the%20Budget%20outside%20the%20assembly.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20does%20go%20for%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20for%20the%202024%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20lose%20a%20critical%20narrative%20it%20crafted%20to%20counter%20dynastic%20politics.%20The%20JD(S)%20is%20a%20family%20party%20with%20at%20least%20seven%20active%20members%20of%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20clan%20with%20electoral%20aspirations.%20Siddaramaiah%20quit%20the%20JD(S)%20in%202005%20over%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20who%20was%20then%20being%20groomed%20as%20the%20heir%20apparent%20of%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20shrinking%20vote%20of%20the%20JD(S)%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20election%20to%2013.3%25%20is%20ascribed%2C%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20to%20Siddaramaiah's%20charisma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20NDA%20forms%20the%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20in%202024%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20can%20easily%20bag%20a%20couple%20of%20ministerial%20berths%2C%20which%20is%20an%20impossible%20dream%20if%20it%20fights%20the%20election%20on%20its%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20political%20compulsions%2C%20this%20'friends-with-benefits'%20relationship%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20will%20last%20only%20until%20one%20of%20them%20seeks%20greener%20pastures%20elsewhere.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690355400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fl85mhdso_modi-kumaraswamy-pti_650x400_28_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-challenges-for-friends-with-benefits-bjp-and-jd-s-4240837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20election%20results%20have%20brought%20together%20strange%20bedfellows%20trying%20to%20forge%20a%20united%20opposition%20in%20the%20state.%20Despite%20ideological%20differences%2C%20the%20proximity%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20is%20growing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-challenges-for-friends-with-benefits-bjp-and-jd-s-4240837%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-challenges-for-friends-with-benefits-bjp-and-jd-s-4240837%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-challenges-for-friends-with-benefits-bjp-and-jd-s-4240837%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dulquer%3A%20Amal%20hasn't%20accepted%20that%20I'm%20an%20actor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690355257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102105301%2Cimgsize-28170.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdulquer-salmaan-my-wife-has-still-not-accepted-the-fact-that-im-an-actor-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F102105380.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102105380.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDulquer%20Salmaan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sincere%20talents%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20he%20is%20someone%20who%20has%20managed%20to%20crossover%20lanaguages%20with%20utmost%20ease%2C%20but%20somehow%20his%20father%20legendary%20Mammootty%20isn't%20happy%20with%20the%20fewer%20films%20he%20does%20every%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jigar%20Shah%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdulquer-salmaan-my-wife-has-still-not-accepted-the-fact-that-im-an-actor-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F102105380.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Baby%20Dies%20in%20Detention%20Centre%2C%20Rohingya%20Family%20Brought%20to%20Last%20Rites%20in%20Handcuffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26122554%2FScreenshot-2023-07-26-at-12.25.33-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Forty-year-old%20Numina%20Begum%20and%20her%20husband%20Muhammad%20Saleem%2C%20Rohingya%20Muslim%20refugees%20lodged%20in%20the%20lone%20detention%20centre%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20were%20brought%20in%20handcuffs%20on%20July%2019%20to%20attend%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20their%20infant%20child.%20While%20the%20Rohingya%20living%20in%20Jammu%20claim%20that%20the%2040-day-old%20baby%20died%20after%20inhaling%20teargas%20fired%20by%20the%20police%20during%20clashes%20between%20detained%20refugees%20and%20the%20detention%20centre%20staff%20on%20July%2018%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20authorities%20denied%20the%20allegation%2C%20saying%20the%20baby%20had%20not%20been%20keeping%20well%20since%20her%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20not%20denied%20the%20use%20of%20teargas%20in%20the%20centre%20where%20the%20baby%20and%20her%20parents%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20death%20of%20a%20Rohingya%20person%20in%20the%20Hira%20Nagar%20detention%20centre%20in%20Kathua%20district%2C%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrought%20in%20handcuffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20videos%20which%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Numina%20Begum%20and%20her%2017-year-old%20son%20can%20be%20seen%20being%20brought%20in%20handcuffs%20to%20attend%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20funeral%20in%20Jammu%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20videos%2C%20a%20policewoman%20is%20seen%20escorting%20Numina%20Begum%20in%20handcuffs%2C%20while%20a%20few%20women%20from%20the%20Rohingya%20community%20are%20consoling%20her.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20shocked%20to%20see%20them%20in%20handcuffs.%20Saleem%20and%20his%20elder%20son%20were%20handcuffed%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20offering%20funeral%20prayers%20for%20the%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20elder%20community%20member%20from%20Rohingya%20refugees%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20kept%20handcuffed%20here%20for%20nearly%20one%20hour%20and%20then%20take%20back%20to%20the%20detention%20centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20even%20hardcore%20criminals%20are%20not%20treated%20like%20this.%20%E2%80%9CAren%E2%80%99t%20we%20(Rohingya)%20humans%3F%20We%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20we%20would%20be%20subjected%20to%20such%20an%20inhuman%20treatment%20in%20India.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20protest%20against%20their%20maltreatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20infant%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20house%20of%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20brother%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20performing%20ablution%20and%20funeral%20prayers%2C%20the%20baby%20was%20buried%20at%20a%20graveyard%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20official%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Prison%20Department%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Rohingya%20refugees%20kept%20in%20the%20holding%20centre%20cannot%20be%20treated%20like%20prisoners.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20movement%20is%20restricted%20in%20a%20particular%20area%20till%20they%20are%20repatriated%20to%20their%20native%20country%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20be%20treated%20like%20prisoners.%20Even%20prisoners%20are%20handcuffed%20only%20when%20there%20is%20apprehension%20of%20their%20escape%20or%20if%20they%20are%20dangerous%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20M.S.%20Lone%2C%20former%20DIG%20Prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Rules%2C%202021%20prohibit%20handcuffing%20of%20a%20child%20alleged%20to%20be%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law.%20This%20raises%20question%20on%20the%20handcuffing%20of%20the%20Rohingya%20couple%E2%80%99s%20elder%20son%2C%20who%20is%20said%20to%20be%2017%20and%20is%20thus%20a%20minor%20as%20per%20Indian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20baby%E2%80%99s%20death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20living%20in%20Jammu%20claim%20that%20the%20baby%20died%20due%20to%20teargas%20canisters%20fired%20by%20the%20police%20after%20clashes%20between%20refugees%20and%20prison%20staff%20on%20July%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20fired%20teargas%20shells%20to%20quell%20protests%20by%20Rohingya%20refugees%20who%20were%20seeking%20their%20release%20from%20the%20detention%20centre%20or%20their%20immediate%20repatriation%20to%20Myanmar%2C%20despite%20the%20persecution%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20truth%20in%20the%20claims%20that%20the%20baby%20died%20due%20to%20inhalation%20of%20teargas%20canisters%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20superintendent%20district%20jail%20Kathua%20and%20in-charge%20holding%20centre%2C%20Koushal%20Kumar.%20However%2C%20officials%20have%20not%20denied%20that%20teargas%20was%20used%20against%20the%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaleem%20arrested%20in%202012%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20relatives%2C%20Saleem%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20Fareed%20Alam%20came%20to%20India%20after%20fleeing%20Myanmar%20in%202012%2C%20when%20it%20saw%20large-scale%20violence%20against%20the%20Rohingya.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20forces%20in%20Myanmar%20were%20killing%20and%20torturing%20us.%20We%20ran%20away%20from%20our%20homes%20to%20save%20our%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Fatima%20Begum%2C%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20sister-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaleem%2C%20she%20said%2C%20started%20doing%20menial%20jobs%20in%20Jammu%20to%20eke%20out%20a%20livelihood%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20felt%20safe%20here%20and%20were%20content.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20our%20miseries%20as%20Saleem%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20He%20did%20not%20have%20a%20refugee%20card%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20immediately%20went%20to%20Delhi%20and%20got%20refugee%20cards%2C%E2%80%9Dshe%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20refugee%20card%20is%20issued%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Fatima%20said%20the%20police%20detained%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20wife%20and%20elder%20son%20along%20with%20more%20than%20150%20refugees%20living%20in%20Jammu%20after%20summoning%20them%20for%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20Rohingya%20refugees%20detained%20were%20sent%20to%20Hira%20Nagar%20jail%2C%20which%20was%20notified%20as%20a%20holding%20centre%20on%20March%205%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20government%20had%20then%20said%20in%20a%20notification%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20illegal%20immigrants%20detected%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20will%20be%20lodged%20in%20the%20said%20holding%20centre%20and%20it%20shall%20be%20ensured%20that%20these%20persons%20are%20physically%20available%20at%20all%20times%20for%20their%20expeditious%20deportation%20as%20soon%20as%20travel%20documents%20are%20issued%20after%20due%20process%20of%20their%20nationality%20verification%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20relatives%2C%20the%20couple%20reunited%20in%20the%20Hira%20Nagar%20detention%20centre%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaleem%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20district%20jail%20Jammu.%20He%20was%20shifted%20to%20Hira%20Nagar%20detention%20centre%20nearly%20two%20months%20after%20Numina%20was%20detained%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fatima%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20two%20more%20children%20at%20the%20detention%20centre%2C%20including%20the%20baby%20who%20died%20on%20July%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%2C%20several%20rightwing%20groups%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20have%20been%20campaigning%20for%20the%20ouster%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20demography%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690354855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26122554%2FScreenshot-2023-07-26-at-12.25.33-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fafter-baby-dies-in-detention-centre-rohingya-family-brought-to-last-rites-in-handcuffs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20family%20and%20other%20refugees%20allege%20that%20the%20baby%20died%20due%20to%20teargas%20fired%20by%20authorities%20at%20the%20detention%20centre%2C%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20government%20has%20denied%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fafter-baby-dies-in-detention-centre-rohingya-family-brought-to-last-rites-in-handcuffs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Confidence%20Motion%3A%20Should%20Government%20Worry%3F%20Numbers%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20newly%20formed%20INDIA%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20along%20with%20Telangana's%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20have%20filed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-kcrs-party-file-no-trust-motion-against-government-in-lok-sabha-amid-parliament-impasse-over-manipur-4240464%5C%22%3Etwo%20separate%20no-confidence%20motions%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20move%20comes%20amidst%20the%20ongoing%20parliamentary%20impasse%20over%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20that%20have%20left%20over%20125%20people%20dead%2C%20thousands%20displaced%20and%20new%20tales%20of%20unspeakable%20horrors%20each%20day.%20The%20conflict%2C%20and%20the%20government's%20inability%20to%20end%20it%20even%20after%20three%20months%20of%20violence%2C%20has%20been%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20continuous%20logjam%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20by%20opposition%20parties%20being%20likely%20to%20fail%20the%20numbers%20test%2C%20they%20argue%20that%20they%20will%20win%20the%20%26quot%3Bbattle%20of%20perception%26quot%3B%20by%20cornering%20the%20government%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20during%20the%20debate.%20The%20opposition%20contends%20that%20this%20strategy%20will%20compel%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20address%20the%20crucial%20matter%20in%20parliament%2C%20despite%20the%20government's%20insistence%20that%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Current%20Numbers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20272%2C%20the%20PM%20Modi's%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20is%20safe%20with%20331%20members.%20The%20BJP%20alone%20has%20303.%20The%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20144%20while%20parties%20like%20KCR's%20BRS%2C%20YS%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20YSRCP%20and%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20BJD%20have%20combined%20strength%20of%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUnderstanding%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20a%20parliamentary%20tool%20used%20by%20the%20opposition%20to%20express%20its%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20government.%20The%20ruling%20party%20must%20then%20prove%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20House%20to%20maintain%20confidence.%20If%20it%20loses%20the%20majority%2C%20the%20government%20will%20fall%20immediately.%20The%20government%20can%20remain%20in%20power%20as%20long%20as%20it%20has%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Opposition's%20Weapon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20used%20as%20a%20strategic%20tool%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20allows%20them%20to%20question%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20highlight%20their%20failures%2C%20and%20discuss%20them%20in%20the%20house.%20This%20motion%20also%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20uniting%20the%20opposition.%20If%20the%20motion%20is%20passed%20in%20the%20House%2C%20the%20entire%20cabinet%2C%20including%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20must%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ELok%20Sabha's%20Exclusive%20Right%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Article%2075%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Cabinet%20is%20collectively%20accountable%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Only%20the%20opposition%20can%20bring%20this%20proposal%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20only%2C%20not%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Any%20party%20in%20parliament%20can%20move%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%2C%20and%20the%20ruling%20government%20must%20prove%20its%20majority%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Procedure%20For%20A%20No-Confidence%20Motion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20brought%20according%20to%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Under%20rules%20198(1)%20and%20198(5)%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20it%20can%20be%20introduced%20only%20after%20the%20Speaker%20has%20called%20upon%20it.%20The%20information%20about%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20House%20has%20to%20be%20given%20in%20writing%20to%20the%20Secretary-General%20by%2010%20am.%20It%20requires%20the%20support%20of%20at%20least%2050%20members%20of%20the%20House.%20If%20the%20motion%20is%20passed%2C%20the%20President%20fixes%20one%20or%20more%20days%20for%20discussion.%20The%20President%20of%20India%20can%20also%20ask%20the%20government%20to%20prove%20its%20majority.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20cabinet%20must%20resign%2C%20or%20else%20it%20will%20be%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EImpact%20Of%20No-Confidence%20Motions%20On%20Previous%20Governments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20no-confidence%20motion%20has%20historically%20been%20used%20as%20a%20form%20of%20protest%20to%20keep%20the%20government%20accountable.%20It%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20toppling%20governments%2C%20especially%20when%20coalition%20governments%20started%20to%20form.%20From%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20the%20country's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202018%2C%20several%20leaders%20have%20faced%20this%20proposal.%20While%20some%20survived%2C%20others%20like%20Morarji%20Desai%2C%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20VP%20Singh%2C%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20saw%20their%20governments%20fall%20due%20to%20no-confidence%20motions.%20The%20last%20no-confidence%20motion%20faced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20NDA%20government%20in%202018%20was%20defeated%20by%20199%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690354740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fcjob5qi_parliament-reuters-generic_625x300_17_January_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Often%20used%20as%20a%20strategic%20tool%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20allows%20them%20to%20question%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20highlight%20their%20failures%2C%20and%20discuss%20them%20in%20the%20house.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-does-a-no-confidence-motion-work-4240688%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%20on%20Bhagwad%20Gita%20scene%20in%20Oppenheimer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690354667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102130192%2Cimgsize-60542.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvarun-dhawan-indirectly-talks-about-the-bhagwad-gita-scene-in-oppenheimer-where-does-the-criticism-go-then%2Farticleshow%2F102130192.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102130192.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVarun%20Dhawan%20reacted%20to%20the%20criticism%20which%20the%20Auschwitz%20analogy%20scene%20in%20'Bawaal'%20has%20got.%20He%20explains%20the%20scene%20and%20also%20indirectly%20talks%20about%20the%20Oppenheimer%