C%20the%20fixture%20is%20reportedly%20likely%20to%20be%20rescheduled%20as%20the%20date%20also%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Navaratri%20festival%20in%20the%20state.%20Considering%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20Navaratri%20is%20celebrated%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20the%20whole%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20security%20agencies%20said%20to%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20logistical%20issues.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%2C%20hence%2C%20is%20reportedly%20looking%20to%20restructure%20the%20itinerary%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20tickets%20for%20the%20high-profile%20match%20have%20already%20been%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20mulling%20the%20options%20that%20we%20have%20and%20a%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20soon.%20We%20have%20been%20told%20by%20the%20security%20agencies%20that%20a%20high-profile%20game%20like%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%2C%20for%20which%20thousands%20of%20travelling%20fans%20are%20expected%20to%20reach%20Ahmedabad%2C%20should%20be%20avoided%20since%20they%20will%20be%20stretched%20because%20of%20Navratri%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20top%20BCCI%20official%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbreaking-india-pakistan-world-cup-game-likely-to-be-rescheduled-oct-15-clashes-with-navratri-start-8860145%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20PTI%20report%2C%20the%20match%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20preponed%20by%20a%20day%2C%20and%20held%20on%20October%2014%20instead.%20As%20per%20NDTV%20sources%2C%20the%20request%20from%20BCCI%20over%20change%20in%20schedule%20has%20already%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20game%20will%20not%20move%20out%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20but%20the%20fans%20will%20still%20need%20to%20change%20their%20travel%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the