nd%20there%20has%20been%20no%20loss%20of%20life.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fwatch-ola-lets-350-cabs-get-flooded-in-noida-despite-repeated-warnings-from-authorities%2Farticleshow%2F102128103.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20to%20Move%20No-Trust%20Vote%3A%20Four%20Tactical%20Advantages%20the%20Opposition%20Might%20Be%20Aiming%20For%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16103200%2FGlimpses_of_the_new_Parliament_Building_in_New_Delhi_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ELeaders%20from%20two%20opposition%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20%E2%80%93%20have%20moved%20no-confidence%20motions%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%20parliament%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%20Parliament%20has%20seen%20an%20impasse%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%2C%20with%20opposition%20parties%20insisting%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20talk%20about%20the%20serious%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20and%20allow%20for%20an%20open%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20recently%20announced%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%2C%20the%20BRS%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20a%20clear%20majority%20in%20parliament%2C%20so%20the%20opposition%20cannot%20be%20hoping%20to%20win%20the%20motion.%20So%20what%20is%20the%20agenda%20behind%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20breaks%20down%20how%20the%20opposition%20may%20be%20trying%20to%20make%20some%20valuable%20points%20by%20filing%20a%20no-confidence%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20It%20helps%20establish%20the%20fact%20that%20governments%20come%20and%20go%20and%20are%20accountable.%20There%20is%20nothing%20%E2%80%98perpetual%E2%80%99%20or%20forever%20about%20any%20government%2C%20even%20if%20it%20has%20won%20a%20majority%2C%20twice%2C%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20The%20prime%20minister%20does%20not%20address%20Parliament%20and%20frequently%20picks%20%E2%80%98address%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99%20modes%2C%20like%20YouTube%20or%20his%20own%20social%20media%20channels%20%E2%80%93%20or%20outside%20Parliament%20%E2%80%93%20as%20stages%20for%20policy%20or%20other%20announcements.%20The%20%E2%80%98temple%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20is%20spoken%20of%20and%20worshipped%2C%20but%20its%20value%20as%20an%20institution%20that%20can%20be%20a%20check%20on%20the%20Executive%20is%20under%20serious%20questioning.%20Global%20Indices%20on%20Democracy%20whether%20V-Dem%2C%20Freedom%20House%20or%20International%20IDEA%20have%20recorded%20the%20decline%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Parliament%20as%20a%20check%20on%20government.%20A%20motion%20like%20this%2C%20how%20it%20is%20handled%2C%20draws%20attention%20to%20the%20institution%20and%20its%20ways%20and%20forces%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20There%20is%20a%20drive%20to%20establish%20which%20opposition%20party%20is%20really%20the%20one%20which%20is%20anti%20BJP.%20There%20is%20a%20vast%20line%20of%20%E2%80%98middlers%E2%80%99%2C%20parties%20like%20BRS%2C%20YSRCP%2C%20BJD%20and%20numerous%20others%2C%20not%20amongst%20the%20new%20NDA%20(38)%20or%20INDIA%20(26)%20parties%20that%20are%20then%20forced%20to%20take%20a%20call%20and%20show%20their%20cards.%20This%20helps%20draw%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Within%20INDIA%20too%2C%20there%20is%20Little%20INDIA%2C%20some%20doubts%20and%20concerns%20about%20certain%20parties%2C%20about%20where%20they%20really%20stand.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20sizeable%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20is%20now%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20which%20way%20things%20will%20go.%20This%20helps%20establish%20who%20is%20standing%20where.%20As%20whatever%20may%20be%20the%20chances%20of%20winning%20it%2C%20no%20government%20can%20take%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20non-seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690353017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16103200%2FGlimpses_of_the_new_Parliament_Building_in_New_Delhi_2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-a-no-confidence-motion-now-four-tactical-advantages-the-opposition-might-be-aiming-for%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%20expectation%20amongst%20the%20opposition%20parties%20that%20it%20will%20be%20won.%20The%20difference%20is%20clear.%20BJP%20commands%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20own%2C%20well%20clear%20of%20the%20272%20mark%20(let%20alone%20majority%20amongst%20those%20present%20and%20voting).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-a-no-confidence-motion-now-four-tactical-advantages-the-opposition-might-be-aiming-for%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20to%20act%20in%20films%3F%20Sakshi%20reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690352554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102128785%2Cimgsize-37328.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fms-dhoni-is-open-to-acting-in-films-reveals-his-wife-sakshi-dhoni-hes-not-camera-shy%2Farticleshow%2F102128785.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102128785.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20is%20open%20to%20acting%20in%20films%2C%20according%20to%20his%20wife%2C%2