institution%20of%20the%20ED%20%E2%80%9Crises%20beyond%20any%20one%20individual%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20notion%20that%20the%20current%20application%20filed%20by%20his%20government%20would%20go%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPowers%20of%20the%20ED%20to%20strike%20at%20those%20who%20are%20corrupt%20and%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20law%20remain%20the%20same.%20ED%20is%20an%20institution%20which%20rises%20beyond%20any%20one%20individual%20and%20is%20focused%20on%20achieving%20its%20core%20objective%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%20to%20investigate%20offences%20of%20money%20laundering%20and%20violations%20of%20foreign%20exchange%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20had%20said%20after%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20partisan%20role%20of%20central%20investigative%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI%20have%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%2C%20with%20opposition%20leaders%20almost%20exclusively%20targeted%20by%20these%20two%20bodies.%20Cases%20registered%20against%20such%20leaders%20also%20tend%20to%20fall%20by%20the%20wayside%20when%20politicians%20jump%20ship%20and%20join%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690351957000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F15174623%2FSKMishra_EDdirector_141120_1200.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-government-mishra-extension-again%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Sanjay%20Karol%20had%20earlier%20in%20July%20allowed%20Mishra%20to%20continue%20in%20his%20post%20till%20July%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-enforcement-directorate-government-mishra-extension-again%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Mocks%20'Barbie'%20Over%20Its%20Anti-