20from%20shortlisted%20candidates%20for%20government%20awards%20to%20avoid%20an%20%E2%80%98award-wapsi-like%20situation%E2%80%99%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20system%20may%20be%20put%20in%20place%20where%20an%20undertaking%20is%20taken%20from%20the%20proposed%20awardee%20citing%20acceptance%20of%20the%20award%20and%20that%20the%20awardees%20cannot%20dishonor%20the%20award%20at%20any%20point%20of%20time%20in%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0stated%20a%20report%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20transport%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20culture%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fparliamentary-committee-recommends-prior-undertakings-from-recipients-cultural-institutions-academies-2411480-2023-07-25%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fnation%2Fwary-of-award-wapsi-parliamentary-committee-wants-undertaking-from-recipients-529065%3F_gl%3D1*d6iqub*_ga*OUJWNVBJbWNyV25nSlBsSy1ONHk2QkVDS3lXaXVOWi1mMzFhdFdUdE5mVHdqZ3FQd0xqREZpMjJnU0VidnA0dg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20quoted%20the%20committee%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAwards%20may%20not%20be%20given%20without%20such%20an%20undertaking.%20In%20the%20event%20that%20the%20awards%20are%20returned%2C%20the%20awardee%20shall%20not%20be%20considered%20for%20such%20an%20award%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20termed%20the%20act%20of%20returning%20awards%20in%20protest%20against%20political%20issues%20%E2%80%9Cdisgraceful%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%20While%20noting%20that%20political%20issues%20are%20outside%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20cultural%20realms%2C%20returning%20awards%2C%20according%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20would%20impact%20the%20overall%20prestige%20and%20reputation%20of%20the%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20panel%20argued%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Creturn%20of%20the%20award%20is%20not%20used%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20political%20protest%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthefederal.com%2Fstates%2Fsouth%2Fkarnataka%2Faward-wapsi-clause-proposal-shocks-literary-cultural-fraternity-in-karnataka%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20is%20titled%20%3Cem%3EFunctioning%20of%20National%20Akademies%20and%20Other%20Cultural%20Institutions%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20from%20September%202015%2C%20eminent%20writers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20and%20other%20prominent%20personalities%20returned%20awards%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20government%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20targeting%20of%20minorities%20and%20the%20spate%20of%20communal%20violence%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20Many%20prominent%20personalities%20also%20returned%20the%20honours%20bestowed%20on%20them%20by%20the%20government%20in%20protest%20specifically%20against%20the%20murders%20of%20rationalists%20like%20M.M.%20Kalburgi%2C%20Govind%20Pansare%20and%20Narendra%20Dabholkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20them%20returned%20the%20plaque%20and%20others%20sent%20back%20the%20cheques%20of%20amounts%20they%20received%20as%20part%20of%20the%20award.%20The%20committee%20said%20it%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20system%20for%20taking%20back%20the%20award.%20Therefore%2C%20cheques%20were%20not%20deposited%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20instance%20of%20%E2%80%9Caward%20wapsi%E2%80%9D%20after%202015%2C%20the%20committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20specifically%20noted%20that%2039%20recipients%20of%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20Awards%20returned%20their%20awards%20in%202015%20to%20protest%20the%20murder%20of%20Kalburgi.%C2%A0%20The%20Committee%20said%20some%20of%20the%20awardees%20who%20had%20returned%20their%20awards%20continued%20their%20association%20with%20the%20Akademi%2C%20serving%20either%20on%20the%20jury%20or%20participating%20in%20the%20Akademi%E2%80%99s%20programmes.%20It%20questioned%20the%20re-engagement%20of%20such%20awardees%20who%20joined%20the%20Akademi%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20insulting%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20quoted%20several%20writers%2C%20filmmakers%2C%20academicians%2C%20theatre%2C%20and%20folk%20personalities%20of%20Karnataka%20who%20termed%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20panel%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-democratic%2C%20an%20assault%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20curtail%20the%20freedom%20to%20protest%20in%20any%20form%20granted%20by%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAwards%20are%20primarily%20being%20conferred%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20achievement%20of%20personality%20in%20the%20specified%20field%20of%20art.%20The%20selection%20of%20the%20person%20is%20based%20on%20recommendation%20of%20a%20jury%20or%20selection%20committee.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20both%20the%20government%20and%20cultural%20institution%20not%20to%20humiliate%20personalities%20they%20chose%20for%20the%20award%20by%20imposing%20conditions.%20Karnataka%20has%20a%20history%20of%20respecting%20the%20creative%20freedom%20of%20cultural%20personalities%20and%20protecting%20them%20from%20any%20autocratic%20and%20undemocratic%20political%20dispensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20noted%20writer%20and%20cultural%20critic%20Baraguru%20Ramachandrappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690351820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fdelhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fimpose-conditions-on-recipients-of-govt-honours-to-prevent-award-wapsi-parliamentary-panel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20transport%2C%20tourism%2C%20and%20culture%20said%20the%20government%20must%20ensure%20that%20the%20'return%20of%20the%20award%20is%20not%2