issions%20records%20from%20three%20of%20the%2012%20Ivy%20Plus%20colleges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20identifies%20three%20main%20factors%20behind%20the%20discrepancy%3A%20a%20bias%20towards%20children%20of%20alumni%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20legacy%20students%20%E2%80%94%20wealthy%20students%20having%20higher%20non-academic%20ratings%2C%20and%20well-to-do%20students%20being%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20recruited%20as%20student-athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20noted%20that%20although%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20Americans%20attend%20these%2012%20colleges%2C%20these%20schools%20have%20an%20outsized%20impact.%20Ivy%20Plus%20graduates%20%26quot%3Baccount%20for%2015%25%20of%20those%20in%20the%20top%200.1%25%20of%20the%20income%20distribution%2C%20a%20quarter%20of%20US%20Senators%2C%20half%20of%20all%20Rhodes%20scholars%2C%20and%20three-fourths%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20justices%20appointed%20in%20the%20last%20half-century%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%20come%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-ends-affirmative-action-colleges-decision-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20effectively%20ended%20race-based%20affirmative%20action%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Insider%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20scrutiny%20from%20lawmakers%20and%20civil%20rights%20groups%20might%20be%20shifting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Feducation%2F4084026-attention-turns-to-legacy-admissions-after-affirmative-action-ruling%2F%5C%22%3Etowards%20wealth%20and%20legacy%20admissions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20inequality%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsupreme-court-affirmative-action-legacy-college-admissions-5d6f34a13045752c6a37db67c66c7d63%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Associated%20Press%20report