felt%20bad%20asking%20for%20money.%20My%20family%20is%20middle-class%2C%20regular%20people.%20So%20I%20tried%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pretty%20into%20fashion%20in%20high%20school%2C%20so%20I%20started%20selling%20clothes%20on%20Poshmark.%20But%20I%20soon%20realized%20that%20Poshmark%20takes%20a%20lot%20in%20fees%3A%20there's%20a%2020%25%20fee%20on%20sales%20over%20%2415.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20moved%20over%20to%20Depop.%20Depop%20charges%20a%20total%20fee%20of%20around%2014%25%20on%20each%20transaction.%20This%20includes%20a%2010%25%20commission%20on%20the%20sale%20price%2C%20plus%20a%203.3%25%20transaction%20fee%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20%240.45%20charge%20for%20each%20item%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20my%20account%20organically%20to%20around%207%2C000%20followers.%20I%20did%20this%20by%20posting%20high-quality%20try-on%20photos%20with%20consistent%20backgrounds%2C%20using%20relevant%20hashtags%2C%20and%20regularly%20refreshing%20my%20posts%20on%20my%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20source%20my%20items%20from%20thrift%20stores%2C%20SSENSE%2C%20and%20other%20popular%20girl%20brands%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20used%20clothing%2C%20I%20like%20to%20source%20from%20thrift%20stores%20%E2%80%94%20Goodwill%20near%20me%20has%20really%20good%20inventory.%20For%20example%2C%20last%20fall%20when%20leather%20jackets%20were%20really%20in%2C%20Goodwill%20was%20selling%20them%20for%20%2420%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20them%20for%20%2480.%20I%20made%20a%20%2450%20profit%20off%20that%2C%20so%20the%20net%20profit%20there%20was%20pretty%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20clothes%2C%20I%20also%20go%20to%20SSENSE%2C%20an%20upscale%20online%20department%20store%20with%20large%20sales%20up%20to%2070%25%20off%20every%20twice%20a%20year.%20It's%20crucial%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20trends%20and%20what's%20in%20demand.%20But%20be%20cautious%20of%20return%20policies%2C%20especially%20final%20sales.%20I%20prefer%20to%20avoid%20those%20because%20I'd%20rather%20repair%20unsold%20items%20than%20hold%20excess%20inventory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20source%20some%20items%20from%20popular%20girl%20brands%20like%20Realization%20Par%2C%20Mirror%20Palais%2C%20and%20other%20department%20stores%20that%20carry%20these%20brands.%20You%20have%20to%20catch%20the%20sales%20because%20these%20items%20are%20usually%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20I%20tried%20to%20buy%20tops%20with%20ribbons%20on%20sale%20from%20these%20stores%20because%20they%20were%20trending%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20went%20to%20Europe%20this%20summer%20and%20saw%20that%20everyone%20was%20wearing%20Silver%20Onitsuka%20Tiger%20Mexico%2066s%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20very%20sought-after%20shoes%20in%20Europe.%20I%20thought%20that%20trend%20would%20carry%20over%20to%20the%20States%2C%20and%20when%20I%20came%20back%20home%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20started%20seeing%20the%20shoes%20on%20my%20TikTok%20feed.%20So%20I%20bought%20a%20few%20of%20those%20and%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20a%20pair%20for%20a%20200%25%20markup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENow%20I'm%20on%20track%20to%20make%20%24100%2C000%20in%20revenue%20this%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20ship%20items%20out%20two%20days%20a%20week%20and%20dedicate%20about%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20to%20printing%20labels%2C%20packing%20everything%20up%2C%20and%20sending%20them%20to%20the%20post%20office%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20check%20my%20Depop%20messages%20every%20morning%20and%20during%20lunch%20to%20see%20if%20anyone's%20interested%20in%20anything.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I'll%20top%20off%20the%20labels%20and%20bundle%20all%20the%20packages%20together%20%E2%80%94%20this%20takes%20about%20an%20hour%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20store%20all%20my%20inventory%20in%20my%20garage%20and%20try%20to%20keep%20things%20organized%3A%20shoes%20in%20one%20section%2C%20arranged%20by%20size%2C%20and%20clothing%20in%20another%2C%20with%20cardigans%20and%20sweaters%20grouped%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20a%20label%20printer%2C%20so%20I%20print%20six%20labels%20on%20one%20page%20using%20my%20computer%20and%20cut%20them%20out.%20If%20it%20gets%20overwhelming%2C%20I'll%20ask%20my%20mom%20to%20help%20with%20the%20cutting%20and%20taping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20shipping%20easier%2C%20I%20sometimes%20schedule%20USPS%20pickups%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20boxes%20to%20the%20post%20office.%20I%20usually%20send%20out%2012-15%20package%20items%203%20times%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBefore%20starting%20Depop%2C%20you%20need%20to%20define%20your%20goals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20selling%20items%3A%20you%20want%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20some%20clothes%20or%20items%20you%20no%20longer%20need%2C%20and%20you%20want%20to%20make%20some%20extra%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20kind%20is%20more%20hardcore%20reselling%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20have%20to%20source%20items%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20usually%20stuff%20that's%20on%20sale%20and%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20become%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20this%20season%2C%20Adidas%20Samba%20shoes%20are%20really%20in%20and%20very%20hard%20to%20get%2C%20and%20the%20popular%20sizes%20for%20women%20are%20seven%20to%20eight.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20find%20items%20that%20are%20trendy%2C%20more%20scarce%2C%20and%20price%20them%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEssential%20tips%20to%20succeed%20as%20a%20Depop%20seller%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Always%20%26quot%3Brefresh%26quot%3B%20your%20items%20and%20use%20hashtags%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20something%20that's%20not%20intuitive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Depop%20didn't%20make%20it%20super%20clear%20for%20sellers%20either.%20You%20need%20to%20constantly%20go%20to%20your%20item%20page%2C%20click%20%26quot%3Bedit%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsave%20changes%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20it%20back%20on%20the%20feed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20I%20post%20an%20Adidas%20item%20today%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it'll%20show%20up%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20feed%20based%20on%20when%20I%20posted%20it.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20other%20people%20will%20start%20posting%20Adidas%20items%2C%20so%20my%20listing%20will%20go%20down%20and%20get%20buried.%20In%20that%20situation%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20refresh%20to%20get%20it%20back%20up%20on%20the%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20you%20need%20to%20use%20hashtags.%20You%20can%20place%20up%20to%20five%20hashtags%20to%20increase%20the%20visibility%20of%20how%20much%20your%20item%20is%20shown.%20Typically%2C%20I'll%20try%20to%20fill%20all%20five%20hashtags%20to%20fit%20into%20some%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Model%20the%20items%20with%20something%20that%20looks%20good%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Theresa%20Sobocinski's%20Depop%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c02fd2bea3440019618c59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22877%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20few%20of%20my%20listings.%3Cp%3ETheresa%20Sobocinski%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20can%20see%20what%20it%20looks%20like%20on%20you%2C%20they%20can%20imagine%20how%20it%20might%20look%20like%20on%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20selling%20a%20top%2C%20I'll%20usually%20pair%20it%20with%20a%20nice%20skirt%20or%20whatever%20looks%20good%20with%20the%20top.%20It%20sells%20better%20this%20way%20than%20if%20you%20just%20placed%20it%20on%20your%20bed%20and%20took%20a%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Friendliness%20is%20key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20try%20to%20respond%20back%20to%20customers%20as%20fast%20as%20I%20can.%20If%20I%20have%20a