finds%20no%20parallel%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Manipur.%20What%20can%20be%20more%20horrific%20for%20women%20and%20girls%20when%20they%20were%20paraded%20naked%2C%20fondled%20and%20tortured%20in%20full%20glare%20of%20the%20people%20and%20media.%20The%20scene%20is%20simply%20heart%20wrenching%20and%20disturbing%E2%80%A6%20The%20most%20painful%20thing%20that%20can%20happen%20to%20a%20woman%20as%20human%20being%20is%E2%80%A6%20when%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20husband%20were%20beaten%20to%20death%20and%20her%20daughter%20gang-raped%20by%20the%20predators%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSCN%20(I-M)%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20significant%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20the%20Naga%20and%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20been%20historically%20rivals%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20spoke%20of%20other%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Manipur%2C%20including%20the%20Naga%20woman%20who%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmercilessly%20killed%20on%205th%20July%2C%202023%2C%20at%20Sawombung%2C%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20by%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20after%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20them%20by%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20these%20hours%20of%20tears%20and%20anguish%2C%20we%20stand%20in%20absolute%20solidarity%20with%20the%20victims%20of%20this%20ethnic%20conflict%20and%20convey%20our%20sympathies%20to%20all%20the%20victims.%20We%20condemn%20such%20sexual%20violence%20and%20killing%20of%20women%20%2F%20girls%20%2F%20child%20in%20the%20strongest%20terms%2C%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690346112000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnscn-i-m-issues-statement-condemning-violence-against-women-in-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22