%20evident.%20And%20voters%20tend%20to%20duck%20the%20immediate%20pain%20of%20tackling%20global%20warming%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20softer%2C%20more%20gradual%2C%20%E2%80%98let%E2%80%99s%20not%20panic%20just%20yet%E2%80%99%20approach.%20Democracy%20may%20well%20be%20the%20best%20form%20of%20government%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20always%20at%20its%20best%20in%20dealing%20with%20%E2%80%98slow%20burn%E2%80%99%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20main%20British%20political%20parties%20are%20getting%20nervous%20all-of-a-sudden%20about%20championing%20the%20green%20agenda.%20They%20have%20been%20spooked%20by%20the%20latest%20spate%20of%20by-elections%20%E2%80%93%20two%20of%20which%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20safe%20Conservative%20seats%20to%20opposition%20parties%2C%20but%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20a%20third%20contest%20in%20a%20seat%20that%20the%20Conservatives%20narrowly%20managed%20to%20retain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20Boris%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20until%20he%20flounced%20off%20after%20being%20found%20out%20as%20a%20serial%20liar.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20lower%20middle%20class%20area%20on%20the%20western%20outskirts%20of%20London.%20All%20political%20observers%20thought%20%E2%80%93%20given%20the%20unpopularity%20of%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20Conservative%20government%20%E2%80%93%20that%20this%20would%20be%20an%20easy%20Labour%20victory.%20They%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reason%3A%20the%20Labour%20Mayor%20of%20London%20is%20about%20to%20introduce%20a%20daily%20charge%20of%20about%20Rs%201%2C250%20for%20anyone%20driving%20an%20old%20and%20high%20polluting%20car%20or%20van%20anywhere%20in%20the%20capital.%20That%E2%80%99s%20on%20top%20of%20the%20Rs%201%2C500%20%E2%80%98congestion%20charge%E2%80%99%20that%20any%20vehicle%20owner%20has%20to%20pay%20for%20every%20day%20they%20bring%20their%20car%20into%20central%20London.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3