o%20are%20celebrated%20by%20multitudes%20of%20women%2C%20and%20keen%20social%20commentators%2C%20BTS%20are%20always%20in%20a%20fighting%20stance%2C%20ready%20with%20proofs%2C%20should%20yet%20another%20doubter%20ask%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20book%2C%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20longtime%20interviewer%20Kang%20Myeongseok%20tells%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20story%20through%20interviews%20he%20conducted%20with%20its%20seven%20members%20through%20the%20past%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20thus%20an%20oral%20history%20of%20the%20tour%20de%20force%20that%20the%20artistes%20have%20been%20%E2%80%93%20marrying%20spoken%20reflections%20with%20a%20dogged%20recounting%20of%20all%20the%20unsavoury%20things%20that%20made%20BTS%20the%20success%20it%20is%20today.%20It%20dives%20deep%20into%20the%20process%20of%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20more%20than%20300%20songs%20that%20the%20band%20has%2C%20taking%20time%20to%20look%20into%20why%20key%20songs%20did%20well%2C%20why%20some%20others%20tanked%20when%20they%20were%20released%2C%20at%20which%20point%20the%20band%20had%20to%20face%20the%20misogyny%20in%20its%20music%2C%20and%20which%20member%20hurt%20a%20knee%20during%20which%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20the%20often%20stirring%20reflections%20by%20RM%2C%20Jin%2C%20SUGA%2C%20j-hope%2C%20Jimin%2C%20V%20and%20Jungkook%2C%20the%20stories%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20the%20Story%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20not%20exactly%20new%20to%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20fans.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20once%20it%20is%20all%20put%20together%20between%20two%20covers%2C%20you%20do%20marvel%20at%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20protest%20that%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20very%20existence%20is.%20Although%20now%20a%20pillar%20of%20the%20South%20Korean%20cultural%20wave%20sweeping%20across%20the%20world%2C%20the%20book%20offers%20a%20solid%20look%20at%20how%20much%20of%20South%20Korean%20dogma%20BTS%20had%20to%20fight%20in%20order%20to%20be%20taken%20seriously%20as%20music%20makers%20and%20performers.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20Asian%20and%20thus%20their%20fame%20and%20talent%20are%20still%20unpalatable%20concepts%20for%20many%20arbiters%20of%20culture%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20the%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fibighit.com%2Fbts%2FBEYOND_THE_STORY%2F%5C%22%3Ebeing%20released%20in%20over%2020%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20three%20English%20translators%2C%20Anton%20Hur%20%E2%80%93%20the%20others%20are%20Slin%20Jung%20and%20Clare%20Richards%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCuiSgrEpUa0%2F%3Figshid%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%253D%253D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20process%20was%20so%20swift%20that%20it%20involved%20translating%20the%20book%20as%20it%20was%20being%20written.%20This%20was%20because%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20company%20HYBE%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmagazine.weverse.io%2Farticle%2Fview%3Fcolca%3D6%26artist%3D%26searchword%3D%26num%3D824%26lang%3Den%5C%22%3Ewas%20keen%20to%20publish%20the%20book%20by%20July%209%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%2010-year%20anniversary%20of%20the%20creation%20of%20its%20fandom%2C%20%E2%80%98ARMY%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20now%20tens%20of%20millions%20strong.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20this%20book%20is%20almost%20a%20singular%20recognition%20of%20how%20this%20enormous%20musical%20presence%20came%20to%20be%20with%20the%20power%20of%20its%20fans.%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20fans%20have%20translated%20their%20work%2C%20analysed%20it%2C%20pushed%20for%20radio%20play%2C%20streamed%20their%20music%2C%20and%20fiercely%20criticised%20racist%20and%20unfair%20critiques.%20In%20the%20book%2C%20members%20of%20the%20band%20note%20this%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20it%20is%20a%20book%20on%20reflections%2C%20its%20pace%20betrays%20the%20urgency%20Hur%20talks%20of%2C%20and%20puts%20you%20on%20edge.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20seven%20chapters%20and%20500%20pages%2C%20you%20are%20angry%20when%20RM%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20rapper%E2%80%99s%20slight%20on%20stage%2C%20anxious%20when%20Jimin%20has%20to%20learn%20to%20set%20his%20voice%20free%20for%20the%20song%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-ThId6ZWqsE%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELie%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20happy%20when%20V%20can%20lean%20on%20his%20elder%20brothers%20for%20strength%2C%20and%20devastated%20when%20the%20band%E2%80%99s%20star%20producer%20SUGA%20decides%20he%20hates%20music%20(he%20does%20roll%20this%20back).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fmin-yoongi-bts-agust-d-suga-jakarta-asia-d-day-tour%5C%22%3EWatching%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20Min%20Yoongi%20in%20the%20Continent%20that%20Made%20Him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20book%20to%20hold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20strength%20of%20%3Cem%3EBeyond%20the%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20lies%20not%20just%20in%20essaying%20a%20story%20of%20seven%20men%2C%20but%20in%20the%20innovation%20it%20has%20brought%20to%20book%20making.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20even%20before%20social%20media%20created%20public%20opinion%2C%20BTS%20and%20its%20company%20BIGHIT%20Music%20were%20circumventing%20a%20low%20marketing%20budget%20by%20uploading%20YouTube%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCLkAepWjdylmXSltofFvsYQ%5C%22%3Evlogs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20writing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBTS_twt%2Fstatus%2F306797064522698752%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etweets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20an%20entirely%20new%20way%2C%20creating%20its%20enormous%20global%20reach.%20Such%20a%20method%20of%20promotion%20was%20alien%20to%20South%20Korean%20entertainment%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20same%20clairvoyance%20that%20has%20perhaps%20led%20to%20the%20production%20of%20a%20book%20that%20can%20pierce%20through%20our%20Reel-addled%20attention%20span%20to%20become%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntonHur%2Fstatus%2F1681915376374775814%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earguably%20the%20second%20ever%20Korean%20volume%20in%20translation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20top%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fbooks%2Fbest-sellers%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENYT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fbooks%2Fbest-sellers%2F%5C%22%3E%20Bestsellers%E2%80%99%20list%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20unveils%20quite%20a%20few%20tactical%20ways%20of%20telling%20a%20story%20with%20seven%20sides%20to%20it%20and%20at%20once%20protecting%20it%20from%20crowding%20with%20the%20use%20of%20simple%20tools.%20The%20seven%20members%E2%80%99%20words%20are%20indented%20and%20in%20grey.%20Kang%E2%80%99s%20flowing%20commentary%20is%20in%20black.%20Lithe%20footnotes%20are%20in%20dark%20blue.%20And%20the%20most%20crucial%20of%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20hundreds%20of%20videos%20and%20songs%20referred%20to%20in%20the%20book%20are%20introduced%20through%20QR%20codes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20thus%20a%20veritable%20item%20to%20collect.%20And%20for%20fans%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20album%20shipping%20process%20is%20long%20and%20expensive%20%E2%80%93%20the%20book%20is%20also%20a%20chance%20to%20own%20something%20authentic%20by%20BTS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EArticle%20on%20Beyond%20the%20Story%20in%20yesterday's%20Loksatta!!%20It's%20a%20Maharasthrian%20publication%20in%20Marathi.%20The%20article%20mainly%20talks%20about%20BTS%20and%20the%20book%20and%20shares%20that%20there%20were%20approx.%205000%20pre-orders%20in%20India.%20It%20describes%20the%20book%20and%20mentions%20the%20band%20is%20maintaining%20a%20connection%2B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0MDdnbBjQo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F0MDdnbBjQo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Illustri%E2%81%B7%20(%40UrsaLune)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUrsaLune%2Fstatus%2F1680606046652596225%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20be%20difficult%20to%20choose%20what%20to%20say%20in%20your%20own%20story.%20In%202009%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20a%20then%20unfinished%20memoir%2C%20the%20American%20poet%20Mary%20Karr%20had%20told%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theparisreview.org%2Finterviews%2F5992%2Fthe-art-of-memoir-no-1-mary-karr%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Paris%20Review%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20circles%20me%20like%20a%20gnat.%20I%20circle%20it%20like%20a%20dog%20staked%20to%20a%20pole.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20the%20narrator%20of%20a%20story%20told%20by%20seven%20people%20about%20seven%20experiences%20of%20their%20one%20shared%20youth%20must%20be%20a%20pretty%20tough%20task.%20Tougher%20yet%20is%20to%20exercise%20choice%20at%20every%20instance%20and%20goad%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20interviews%20into%20linear%20shape.%20Kang%20does%20this%20with%20a%20fair%20degree%20of%20success.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKang%20heads%20the%20%3Cem%3EWeverse%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EMagazine%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20published%20by%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20own%20company.%20Celebrated%20as%20a%20music%20writer%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20not%20much%20is%20known%20of%20him%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20other%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20the%20one%20journalist%20to%20whom%20all%20seven%20very%20private%20members%20of%20BTS%20have%20given%20lengthy%20interviews%2C%20full%20of%20passionate%20talk%20on%20what%20goes%20into%20their%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20book%2C%20especially%20magical%20are%20points%20where%20his%20personal%20fondness%20for%20the%20seven%20BTS%20members%20sneak%20in.%20One%20such%20moment%20is%20when%20Kang%20speaks%20of%20BTS%E2%80%99s%20performance%20leader%20j-hope%E2%80%99s%20reaction%20to%20a%20brutal%20instance%20of%20mistreatment%20faced%20by%20the%20band%20in%20its%20early%20years.%20He%20writers%20that%20j-hope%20usually%20keeps%20his%20tone%20consistent%20in%20interviews%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20point%20of%20appearing%20as%20an%20objective%20observer%20of%20his%20own%20life%20%E2%80%93%20but%20that%20%E2%80%9Csometimes%2C%20very%20rarely%2C%20j-hope%E2%80%99s%20voice%20fills%20with%20emotion.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20a%20simple%20paragraph%2C%20rendered%20perfectly%20in%20translation%2C%20but%20laden%20with%20meaning%20for%20fans%20of%20the%20band%20who%20know%20indeed%20how%20rare%20and%20thus%20precious%20this%20glimpse%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690338649000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25212630%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-9.25.31.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbts-beyond-the-story-book-review-kang-myeongseok%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20oral%20history%20of%20the%20biggest%20contemporary%20musical%20act%20in%20the%20world%20is%20marketed%20not%20as%20an%20autobiography%20or%20a%20memoir%2C%20but%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98proof%E2%80%99%20of%20its%20first%20ten%20years.%20Here's%20why%20this%20works.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbts-beyond-the-story-book-review