0(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202022%2C%20was%20passed%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20without%20discussion%2C%20opposition%20MPs%20raised%20slogans%20through%20the%20proceedings%2C%20holding%20banners%20that%20read%20%E2%80%9CSave%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%20and%20calling%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20to%20address%20the%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20Shah%20tweeted%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20said%20that%20he%20has%20urged%20both%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Crise%20above%20party%20lines%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccooperate%E2%80%9D%20on%20this%20important%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20I%20wrote%20to%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20both%20houses%2C%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadhirrcinc%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40adhirrcinc%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40kharge%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20appealing%20to%20them%20for%20their%20invaluable%20cooperation%20in%20the%20discussion%20of%20the%20Manipur%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20of%20Manipur%20and%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIpGGtYSNwT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIpGGtYSNwT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Shah%20(%40AmitShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1683826545725677574%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203%2C%20in%20which%2