an%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELok%20Sabha%20passes%20Bill%20by%20voice%20vote%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20discussed%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment%20Bill)%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20July%2025.%20Today%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%E2%80%9D%20Bill%20is%20being%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%2C%20Yadav%20said.%20He%20added%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Significant%E2%80%99%20because%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20undergoing%20a%20triple%20crisis%20now.%20On%20one%20side%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20on%20another%20is%20the%20crisis%20of%20desertification%20of%20land%2C%20and%20on%20the%20third%2C%20the%20crisis%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20biological%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20country%2C%20we%20want%20to%20promote%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%A6by%20%5Bdecriminalising%20offences%5D%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20and%20ease%20of%20living%20is%20being%20brought%20forward%20by%20this%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20spoke%20right%20through%20loud%20protests%20%E2%80%93%20by%20the%20opposition%20pertaining%20to%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20by%20voice%20vote%20later%20and%20the%20House%20adjourned%20till%205%20pm%20immediately%20after%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Biological%20Diversity%20Amendment%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20will%20amend%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20the%20conservation%20of%20biological%20diversity%20in%20India%20and%20their%20sustainable%20use%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fair%20and%20equitable%20sharing%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20arise%20from%20using%20biodiversity.%20It%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2016%2C%202021%2C%20by%20Yadav.%20Experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbiodiversity-amendments-further-isolate-agriculture-environment-ministries%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eargued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Bill%20encourages%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20investments%20%E2%80%93%20promotes%20%E2%80%9Cease%20of%20doing%20business%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20simplifies%20the%20patent%20application%20process%2C%20and%20that%20it%20will%20further%20alienate%20India%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20and%20environment%20ministries.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20concern%20that%20the%20Bill%20will%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20and%20AYUSH%20practitioners%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%2C%20following%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvidhilegalpolicy.in%2Fresearch%2Fcomments-to-the-joint-committee-on-parliament-on-the-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-2021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriticisms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20chaired%20by%20Sanjay%20Jaiswal.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20on%20August%202%2C%202022.%20Some%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20has%20addressed%20several%20points%20raised%20by%20critics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOur%20major%20submission%20was%20reg.%20the%20ambiguous%20definition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20controlled%20company%E2%80%9D%20which%20would%20have%20changed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act%20altogether.%20Glad%20that%20the%20report%20not%20just%20discusses%20this%20point%20but%20accepting%20our%20suggestion%20of%20S2(27)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FR8t42n0Wvj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FR8t42n0Wvj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Debadityo%20Sinha%20(%40debadityo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdebadityo%2Fstatus%2F1554507332603691008%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%202%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20committee%20accepted%20several%20amendments%20%E2%80%93%20including%20ones%20that%20exempt%20users%20of%20codified%20traditional%20knowledge%20from%20sharing%20benefits%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiological-diversity-bill-passed-amid-opposition-protests-on-manipur-violence-101690279400291.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20experts%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvidhilegalpolicy.in%2Fresearch%2Fcomments-to-the-joint-committee-on-parliament-on-the-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-2021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20concerns%20about%20the%20Bill%20decriminalising%20offences%20under%20the%20Act%20and%20making%20them%20punishable%20only%20with%20a%20penalty%20(between%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20continuing%20violations%20can%20attract%20an%20additional%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore)%20and%20no%20imprisonment.%20The%20committee%20merely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbilltrack%2Fprs-products%2Fjpc-report-summary%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Bill%2520was%2520introduced%2520in%2Cassociated%2520knowledge%2520with%2520local%2520communities.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20penalty%20structure%20should%20not%20be%20too%20meagre%20as%20it%20could%20enable%20violators%20to%20escape%20with%20a%20small%20fine.%20It%20recommended%20that%20the%20penalty%20should%20be%20proportionate%20to%20the%20gains%20obtained%20by%20entities%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690294840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25193917%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-7.38.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bill%20was%20cleared%20amidst%20loud%20protests%20by%20the%20opposition%20regarding%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20Multi-Crore%20Biz%20Is%20on%20a%20Mission%20To%20Make%20Millet-Based%20Healthy%20Snacks%20Affordable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERaju%20Bhupati%20recalls%20that%20his%20inspiration%20to%20work%20for%20access%20to%20better%20nutrition%20in%20India%20was%20his%20father.%20%E2%80%9C%5BMy%20father%5D%20was%20a%20homoeopathic%20practitioner%20and%20would%20treat%20the%20poor%20for%20free.%20This%20was%20the%20base%20for%20my%20motivation%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20nutrition%20challenge%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20then%2C%20delivering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322864%2Fkochi-aathira-sethumadhavan-pcos-weight-loss-healthy-diet-nutrition-sustainable-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaste%20and%20nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20keeping%20our%20offerings%20affordable%20for%20all%20of%20India%20has%20been%20of%20utmost%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raju%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Amalapuram%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Raju%20worked%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20for%20several%20years%20in%20the%20US.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20as%20the%20global%20delivery%20head%20of%20a%20large%20firm%20to%20pursue%20his%20entrepreneurial%20dream.%20This%20journey%20began%20with%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20that%20he%20ran%20till%202017.%20After%20selling%20it%20that%20year%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20food%20and%20nutrition%20were%20two%20areas%20he%20wanted%20to%20continue%20to%20focus%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20how%20Hyderabad-based%20Troo%20Good%2C%20a%20millet%20snack%20company%2C%20was%20formed%20in%202018.%20It%20sells%20around%202%20million%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eper%20day%2C%20and%20is%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20millet%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChikki%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20nutri-bars%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chikkis%20being%20made%20at%20a%20Troo%20Good%20facility%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchikkis-1690291789-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChikkis%20being%20made%20at%20one%20of%20Troo%20Good%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20facilities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20food%20affordable%2C%20I%20needed%20something%20locally%20available.%20Quinoa%20is%20a%20good%2C%20healthy%20alternative%20to%20wheat%2C%20but%20it%20is%20expensive%20and%20has%20to%20be%20imported.%20Then%20I%20found%20millets%2C%20which%20are%20the%20best%20choice.%20They%20are%20as%20economical%20as%20wheat%2C%20but%20much%20more%20nutritious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organization%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20(FAO)%20says%20that%20millets%20provide%20antioxidants%2C%20minerals%2C%20fibre%2C%20iron%20and%20protein%2C%20alongside%20being%20gluten-free%20with%20a%20low-glycaemic%20index.%20Millets%20are%20also%20economical%20as%20they%20require%20less%20water%20and%20fewer%20pesticides%2C%20and%20are%20also%20climate%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20explains%20that%20he%20began%20his%20journey%20with%20selling%20millet%20parathas%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20the%20same%20taste%20and%20higher%20nutrition%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20normal%20wheat-based%20paratha%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20selling%20Hello%20Curry%2C%20I%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eparathas%20to%20local%20schools%20and%20corporations%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2047-year-old%2C%20adding%20that%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20demand%20eventually%20became%20an%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20began%20with%20selling%201%2C000%20parathas%20a%20month%2C%20he%20scaled%20up%20to%2090%2C000%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20three%20months.%20However%2C%20another%20challenge%20was%20the%20short%20shelf%20life%20of%20the%20parathas%2C%20alongside%20the%20fact%20that%20Raju%E2%80%99s%20venture%20was%20bootstrapped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20manage%20the%20demand%2C%20I%20would%20need%20a%20humongous%20distribution%20network.%20I%20decided%20to%20shift%20focus%20to%20something%20with%20a%20higher%20shelf%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20gave%20birth%20to%20the%20hugely%20popular%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBetting%20on%20the%20humble%20millet%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raju%20Bhupati.%20Founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20Troo%20Good%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117.jpeg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117-768x1153.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117-1023x1536.jpeg%201023w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraju-bhupati-1690292117-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325154%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaju%20Bhupati%2C%20Founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20Troo%20Good.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Rs%205%20and%2010%20snack%20market%20is%20huge.%20You%20mostly%20get%20chips%2C%20biscuits%20and%20other%20snacks%20in%20that%20price%20range.%20I%20saw%20that%20existing%20options%20only%20cater%20to%20taste.%20I%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20three%20fundamentals%20through%20Troo%20Good%20%E2%80%94%20affordability%2C%20taste%20and%20nutrition.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20millet%20parathas%20were%20already%20such%20a%20hit%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20how%20the%20grains%20could%20be%20turned%20into%20snacks.%20He%20then%20found%20the%20%3Cem%3Echikki%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20higher%20shelf%20life%2C%20to%20be%20a%20perfect%20vessel%20to%20help%20him%20with%20his%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20in-house%20team%20of%20scientists%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314758%2Fmothers-start-rigdam-foods-ready-to-eat-millet-snacks-for-children-earn-turnover-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformulated%20the%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20contains%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20peanuts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20improved%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20this%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%20due%20to%20food%20fortification.%20Food%20fortification%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20adding%20essential%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20to%20commonly%20consumed%20foods%20during%20processing%20to%20increase%20their%20nutritional%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20A%20Laxmaiah%2C%20former%20scientist%20G%20(Director%20Grade%20Scientist)%20%26amp%3B%20head%2C%20Division%20of%20Public%20Health%20Nutrition%3B%20head%20Research%20and%20Development%20and%20Quality%2C%20Troo%20Good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHiring%2C%20producing%2C%20and%20selling%20locally%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2280%20percent%20of%20Troo%20Good's%20factory%20employees%20are%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good3-1690292201-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325157%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEighty%20percent%20of%20Troo%20Good%E2%80%99s%20factory%20employees%20are%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20%3C%2Fem%3E(NFHS-5)%202019-21%2C%20undernutrition%20remains%20a%20big%20problem%20among%20children.%20If%20we%20take%20the%20example%20of%20Chattisgarh%2C%20the%20survey%20found%20that%2031.3%25%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%205%20are%20underweight%20and%2034.6%25%20are%20stunted.%20The%20study%20also%20found%20that%20girls%2C%20women%2C%20and%20young%20mothers%20are%20anaemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTroo%20Good%E2%80%99s%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20protein%2C%20iron%2C%20and%20beta-carotene.%20For%20children%2C%20the%20consumption%20of%20this%20wondergrain%20helps%20battle%20deficiency%20diseases%20like%20Bitot%E2%80%99s%20spots%2C%20night%20blindness%2C%20corneal%20ulcers%2C%20keratomalacia%2C%20anaemia%2C%20and%20helps%20in%20growth%20and%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20A%20Laxmaiah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETroo%20Good%20sells%20these%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20schools%20across%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20are%20dealing%20with%20a%20major%20issue%20of%20malnutrition.%20I%20found%20that%20millets%20could%20be%20a%20panacea%20for%20solving%20the%20nutrition%20issue%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raju%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20first%20began%20their%20operations%20in%202018%2C%20Troo%20Good%20started%20by%20selling%20100%20kg%20a%20day.%20In%20September%2C%20a%20sudden%20uptick%20in%20demand%20meant%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20produce%20at%20least%205%2C000%20kg%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20outsource%20our%20production%2C%20so%20scaling%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge%20for%20us.%20I%20believe%20in%20hiring%20locals%2C%20procuring%20raw%20material%20locally%2C%20producing%20locally%20and%20selling%20locally.%20Suddenly%20a%20tsunami%20hit%20us%20in%20terms%20of%20demand%20and%20we%20were%20not%20prepared.%20We%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20infrastructure.%20We%20needed%20to%20add%20at%20least%20three%20new%20factories%20in%2010%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raju.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20he%20booked%20buses%20and%20sent%20his%20employees%20to%20remote%20places%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20nearby%20states.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20skilled%20manpower.%20My%20team%20members%20went%20to%20villages%20and%20spent%20nights%20in%20the%20houses%20of%20contractors.%20We%20had%20to%20add%20factories%20at%20lightning%20speed.%20With%20a%20ton%20of%20courage%2C%20we%20added%20three%20factories%20in%2015%20days%20and%20increased%20our%20volumes%20to%205%2C000%20kgs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20CEO%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20then%20scaled%20to%2030%2C000%20kg%2C%20and%20so%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20adds%20that%20by%20producing%20themselves%2C%20they%20are%20able%20to%20have%20higher%20margins%2C%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20employment.%20They%20have%20five%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Chattisgarh.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2053%20crore%20in%20FY%202022-23%2C%20they%20are%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20revenue%20in%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20sold%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271562%2Fchennai-woman-sells-ready-to-eat-snack-mixes-from-ancient-grains%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40%20crore%20millet%20%3Cem%3Echikkis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eso%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20aid%20in%20operations%2C%20they%20also%20hire%20locally%20and%20work%20with%20self-help%20groups%2C%20with%2080%25%20of%20their%20factory%20workers%20being%20women%2C%20according%20to%20Raju.%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20go%2C%20we%20train%20the%20women%20at%20the%20self-help%20groups.%20We%20also%20help%20farmers%20by%20directly%20buying%20from%20them%2C%20helping%20them%20increase%20their%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20water%2C%20one%20%3Cem%3Echikki%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Troo%20Good%20has%20sold%2040%20crore%20millet%20chikkis%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftroo-good-1690292335-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325161%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETroo%20Good%20has%20sold%2040%20crore%20millet%20chikkis%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20currently%20working%20with%20the%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Chattisgarh%20state%20governments%20on%20multiple%20initiatives%20including%20child%20welfare%2C%20young%20mothers%20welfare%20and%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20scheme.%20They%20have%20also%20tied%20up%20with%20The%20Akshaya%20Patra%20Foundation%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Vedanta%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20supplement%20nutrition%20in%20the%20Anganwadis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20farm%20to%20fork%20approach%2C%20the%20company%20works%20with%20about%2015%2C000%20farmers%20in%20these%20states%20directly.%20Raju%20says%20that%20Troo%20Good%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277456%2Fmillet-man-of-telangana-veer-shetty-biradar-ss-bhavani-foods%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargest%20purchaser%20of%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20farmer-friendly%20crops%20and%20also%20beneficial%20to%20the%20environment.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ENABARD%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%2C%20millets%20can%20be%20cultivated%20in%20areas%20that%20have%20low%20rainfall%20and%20poor%20soil%20fertility.%20The%20report%20adds%20that%20millets%20are%20tolerant%20to%20drought%20and%20have%20higher%20nutrient%20content%20compared%20to%20major%20cereal%20crops%20and%20ensure%20food%20and%20nutrition%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20says%20th