s%20Pixxel%20notes%20on%20their%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CIdentifying%20these%20resources%20will%20be%20the%20precursor%20to%20building%20infrastructure%20in%20space%20that%20will%20shift%20heavy%20industry%20away%20from%20earth.%20Thereby%20giving%20us%20a%20realistic%20shot%20at%20reclaiming%20our%20planet%20from%20the%20irreversible%20effects%20of%20climate%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPixxel%20monitors%20the%20%E2%80%98pulse%20of%20the%20planet%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201059px)%20100vw%2C%201059px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221059%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20captured%20by%20Pixxel's%20satellite%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902.jpeg%201059w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902-300x130.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902-500x217.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902-768x333.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902-150x65.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324709%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20image%20captured%20using%20Pixxel%E2%80%99s%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20satellite%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAwais%20adds%20that%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20information%20captured%20by%20the%20satellites%2C%20it%20can%20help%20companies%20make%20better%20decisions%20for%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20when%20fertiliser%20companies%20buy%20our%20data%2C%20they%20can%20find%20out%20where%20nitrogen%20is%20lacking%20in%20the%20soil%20by%20using%20a%20nutrient%20map.%20Companies%20can%20also%20check%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20crops%20and%20identify%20areas%20where%20crop%20diseases%20are%20more%20prevalent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20clients%20are%20spread%20across%20various%20fields%20like%20agriculture%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%20mining%20and%20environmental%20businesses.%20Australian%20cloud-based%20agritech%20company%20DataFarming%20is%20one%20of%20Pixxel%E2%80%99s%2050%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20well%20serviced%20by%20multispectral%20data%20for%20over%2020%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20have%2028%2C000%20farms%20regularly%20accessing%20the%20DataFarming%20platform.%20However%2C%20when%20we%20want%20to%20dig%20deeper%2C%20there%20are%20two%20main%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20spatial%20resolution%20and%20spectral%20resolution.%20As%20farm%20sizes%20increase%20and%20we%20move%20into%20the%20age%20of%20automation%2C%20technology%20is%20going%20to%20need%20to%20fill%20the%20gap%20of%20determining%20crop%20issues%20earlier.%20And%20this%20is%20where%20hyperspectral%20data%20and%20parallel%20research%20come%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tim%20Neale%2C%20Managing%20Director%20at%20DataFarming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPixxel%20has%20launched%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323066%2Fchandrayaan-3-the-history-of-how-india-began-one-of-its-most-significant-space-journeys%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20satellites%20%3C%2Fa%3Eso%20far%20and%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20launch%20six%20more%20early%20next%20year.%20In%20April%202022%2C%20it%20launched%20%E2%80%98Shakuntala%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20SpaceX%20Falcon-9%20rocket%2C%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20companies%20to%20launch%20a%20commercial%20satellite.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20Pixxel%20launched%20it%E2%80%99s%20